©In Loving Memory of Barbara Alice Harper
1934 2015
She was passionate about her gardening and enjoyed sharing
her love of nature and wildlife with family and friends"¼
®For Mary Crawford, Friend and CPG volunteer
She donated the grapefruit tree in the north corner
which was started from a pip in 1948
by her Aunt Queenie, Mrs EE Bell."Č
