┐Jan Mathews
The key was turned, the gates were opened wide
St Peter and woman walked inside and there
within the sunshine of the throne,
She saw the little Garden she had grown
1939-2010"╚
┼In memory of
Dr Thomas Schofield
who worked in Queen Square from 2004-2010
All of old. Nothing else ever. Ever tried. Ever failed
No matter. Try again. Fail again
Fail better
(Samuel Beckett)"č
